title: LF someone to play some casual norms with :)
body:
I've recently hit level 30 and league is getting kind of sucky on my own.
Wouldn't mind someone to play with a bit :)

My game name is JWhizz, add me on there or just comment and I can add you
I prefer to play jungle but I honestly don't mind where I play. Tips are always appreciated too.

Thanks, JWhizz :)

Champs I can play moderately okay:
